PathOfBuilding.Notes:
Simplified crafting notes
Weapon , fractured chaos damage over time, use fossils to get +1 all spell gems, do what you gotta do to clear the wand of caster mods, cannot roll attack mods aug phys pray and multi mod. More cast speed and chaos damage over time are crucible mods
Shield buy something similar its probaby cheaper if you want to make it from scratch get a avoid ailment shield and spam some life essence til you get desired ES/evasion mods. You can aug life for regen but its really expensive. you can also veiled chaos the bottom and get curse effect and craft whatever.
Amulet Get +1 phys fracture, spam chaos damage til damage overtime, lock suffix reforge speed, lock suffix ashling for life craft mod.
Helm : spam some essence
Boots get suppression fracture spam str til regen, lock suffix veiled chaos craft life
Belt fractured flask effect spam cold essence til you flask charges gained craft flask charge duration then use harvest more likely til you hit decent numbers, suffix cannot change aug life for decent life or you can just craft it here.
